 // Programing principles
        // D.R.Y  --> Do Not Repeat Yourself
           // For-loops
          // Methods
         // Inheritance

        // Y.A.G.N.I --> You Aren't Gonna Need it
            // Unnecessary functions
           // Unnecessary variables
          // Does NOT solve the problem
         // Easier ways to solve problem

     // M.I.M.C  --> More is More Complex
          // More code < More to read > more to learn
         // Bigger project > Bigger headaches
        // Forgetfulness from scope

    // K.I.S.S  --> Keep it Super(stupid) Simple
           // Do NOT overcomplicate easy solutions
          // Makes code easier to maintain
         // Time, energy saver
        // Code Readability

